snippet.title: Witch It - PlayStation®5 - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Witch It is now available on PlayStation®5 
Get it at the PS Store: https://store.playstation.com/product/UP8748-PPSA24716_00-0175916715437740
Witch It is a multiplayer hide & seek game. 
Hunters are tasked with seeking hidden witches that blend in with the environment - trust no furnishing, grocery, or utensil!
